@title Multisignature wallet - Allows multiple parties to agree on transactions before execution.
 @author Stefan George - <stefan.george@consensys.net>
nodes.name: MultiSigWallet

nodes.documentation: @dev Fallback function allows to deposit ether.

@dev Allows to add a new owner. Transaction has to be sent by wallet.
 @param owner Address of new owner.
nodes.name: addOwner

nodes.documentation:
@dev Allows to remove an owner. Transaction has to be sent by wallet.
 @param owner Address of owner.
nodes.name: removeOwner
replaceOwner

nodes.documentation:
@dev Allows to change the number of required confirmations. Transaction has to be sent by wallet.
 @param _required Number of required confirmations.
nodes.name: changeRequirement
submitTransaction

nodes.documentation:
@dev Allows an owner to confirm a transaction.
 @param transactionId Transaction ID.
nodes.name: confirmTransaction

nodes.documentation:
@dev Allows an owner to revoke a confirmation for a transaction.
 @param transactionId Transaction ID.
nodes.name: revokeConfirmation

nodes.documentation:
@dev Allows anyone to execute a confirmed transaction.
 @param transactionId Transaction ID.
nodes.name: executeTransaction
isConfirmed
addTransaction
getConfirmationCount
getTransactionCount

nodes.documentation:
@dev Returns list of owners.
 @return List of owner addresses.
nodes.name: getOwners
getConfirmations
getTransactionIds

nodes.documentation:
@title Multisignature wallet with daily limit - Allows an owner to withdraw a daily limit without multisig.
 @author Stefan George - <stefan.george@consensys.net>
nodes.name: MultiSigWalletWithDailyLimit

nodes.documentation:
@dev Allows to change the daily limit. Transaction has to be sent by wallet.
 @param _dailyLimit Amount in wei.
nodes.name: changeDailyLimit

nodes.documentation:
@dev Allows anyone to execute a confirmed transaction or ether withdraws until daily limit is reached.
 @param transactionId Transaction ID.
nodes.name: executeTransaction
isUnderLimit

nodes.documentation:
@dev Returns maximum withdraw amount.
 @return Returns amount.
nodes.name: calcMaxWithdraw
